Package: HelloRanges
Type: Package
Title: Introduce *Ranges to bedtools users
Version: 0.0.3
Author: Michael Lawrence
Maintainer: Michael Lawrence <michafla@gene.com>
Description: Translates bedtools command-line invocations to R code
             calling functions from the Bioconductor *Ranges
             infrastructure. This is intended to educate novice
             Bioconductor users and to compare the syntax and
             semantics of the two frameworks.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: docopt
Depends:
    methods,
    BiocGenerics,
    S4Vectors (>= 0.11.4),
    IRanges (>= 2.7.8),
    GenomicRanges (>= 1.25.5),
    Biostrings (>= 2.41.3),
    BSgenome,
    GenomicFeatures,
    VariantAnnotation (>= 1.19.3),
    GenomicAlignments,
    rtracklayer (>= 1.33.7),
    GenomeInfoDb
Suggests:
    HelloRangesData,
    BiocStyle
    